data.description: This charming home located in the Seatack area of Virginia Beach was completely renovated in 2015. Located in the highly sought after First Colonial school district this home is centrally located near the beach, walking paths, shopping, bases and highways! This 4 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom home is almost 2,000 square feet and has a huge addition with tons of upgrades such as granite countertops in the kitchen, stainless steel appliances and ceramic tile floors. The open floor plan is great for entertaining friends and family. The spacious primary bedroom has a huge bathroom and a large walk in closet. The backyard offers privacy and the front yard is spacious. Don’t miss out on your chance to own the amazing home! Schedule your showing today!
